    "body": "I've hit this error in a fork test that sets the balance of an ERC20 token. The Keccak256 of the account and slot gave a slot index of `0x0c366de881fd9bce507eb22745daf5d962e71b66355fed5e4b8582588bfcd00b`.\r\n\r\nCalling `setStorageAt` with this index fails with `InvalidArgumentsError: Errors encountered in param 1: Invalid value \"0x0c366de881fd9bce507eb22745daf5d962e71b66355fed5e4b8582588bfcd00b\" supplied to : QUANTITY`\r\n",
