    "body": "I just saw the network helpers comment. I can confirm replacing my `setStorageAt` function below with the version from `@nomicfoundation/hardhat-network-helpers` resolved the problem.\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nexport const setStorageAt = async (address: string, index: string, value: string): Promise<void> => {\r\n    const { ethers } = await import(\"hardhat\")\r\n\r\n    await ethers.provider.send(\"hardhat_setStorageAt\", [address, index, value])\r\n    await ethers.provider.send(\"evm_mine\", []) // Just mines to the next block\r\n}```",
